(or real) HTTP server. What happens when you do this? 
 
DNS request is captured by ApateDNS, HTTP GET in Wireshark to port 80, INetSim logs an 
HTTP request and returns a response. This proves DNS interception + HTTP emulation chain 
works and a default image is shown despite using any url. 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 

Q2. Send another request for a web page through HTTPS. What do you notice?

because the emulated serverâ€™s certificate is not trusted.
